      "The Proverbs 31 woman speaks with wisdom and kindness. I declare that this standard is alive and active in mothers today.",
      "Children will arise and call their mothers blessed. The seeds planted in love will bear fruit for generations.",
      "Motherhood is not a burden — it is a calling. It is one of the most powerful platforms for shaping the future that God has ever created.",
      "QUOTE: A mother's prayer in the secret place can reach further than any public platform. Her knees shape nations.",
