      "QUOTE: Of His kingdom there shall be no end. You are building for eternity. Nothing you do for this King is wasted.",
      "PROPHETIC: I declare that divine assignments are being announced over my life in this season. Like Mary, I receive them with faith, and the Holy Spirit is empowering me to bring them to fulfillment."
