      "God became a baby — the Creator became a creation. That act of humility is the foundation of my salvation.",
      "After this night, nothing was ever the same. And because of Christ, nothing in my life will ever be the same.",
      "QUOTE: The silence before the cry was sacred. It was the last breath the world took before God entered it as one of us.",
      "QUOTE: She wrapped the Creator in swaddling clothes. The infinite, held in the arms of the finite. That is Christmas.",
