      "Father, as this sacred season begins, fix my eyes on the cross. Let me not be distracted from the magnitude of what Christ endured.",
      "Holy Spirit, let the steadfastness of Jesus inspire my own commitment. He walked toward the hardest path out of love.",
      "Father, the cross was not an accident — it was a mission planned before the foundation of the world. I worship Your sovereign plan.",
      "Lord, Your love is set like flint. It does not waver, does not retreat, and will never let me go."
